title: Number 1 Alabama?
description:
Wendi Nix, Sam Acho, and Greg McElroy take a look at preseason rankings and discuss whether or not Alabama deserves to be number one. The crew also discuss how Florida plans to rebuild, Notre Dame's chances at the CFP, and notable coaching changes in college football.
